  <brief_title>Cognitive Function and Patient-Reported Quality of Life Outcomes Investigation in Patients Taking Vorinostat</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cognitive Function and Patient-Reported Psychological and Functional/Quality of Life Outcomes Investigation in Patients Taking Vorinostat for Graft-versus-Host Disease Prophylaxis</official_title>
